sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Bot
    participant RAG as "RAG (search helper)"
    participant Convex as "Convex (catalog memory)"
    participant AI as "AI (answer writer)"

    Note over User,Bot: 6-message chat: greeting -> product list question -> price question

    Note over User,Bot: Messages 1-2 (Hello and welcome)
    User->>Bot: "Hello"
    Bot->>Convex: Save the message and read recent chat
    Bot->>RAG: Find helpful catalog context (if any)
    RAG->>Convex: Check stored product knowledge
    Convex-->>RAG: Matching info
    RAG->>AI: Write a polite reply in the same language
    AI-->>RAG: Draft reply
    RAG-->>Bot: Final reply text
    Bot->>Convex: Save bot reply
    Bot-->>User: "Welcome, how can I help today?"

    Note over User,Bot: Messages 3-4 (User asks what categories exist)
    User->>Bot: "What products do you have?"
    Bot->>Convex: Save message + load recent context
    Bot->>RAG: Find the best matching catalog items
    RAG->>Convex: Read product/category data
    Convex-->>RAG: Product facts
    RAG->>AI: Turn facts into a clear list
    AI-->>RAG: List response
    RAG-->>Bot: Final category answer
    Bot->>Convex: Save bot reply
    Bot-->>User: List of available categories + follow-up question

    Note over User,Bot: Messages 5-6 (User asks price for one item)
    User->>Bot: "How much is the wrapped table set?"
    Bot->>Convex: Save message + load recent context
    Bot->>RAG: Find exact product and available options
    RAG->>Convex: Read variant details and prices
    Convex-->>RAG: Standard/Premium details and prices
    RAG->>AI: Write a simple pricing answer
    AI-->>RAG: Price response
    RAG-->>Bot: Final pricing text
    Bot->>Convex: Save bot reply
    Bot-->>User: Price options (for example: Standard vs Premium)
